      "role": "user",
      "content": "1200mg of ibuprofen every few hours?? wow ok. i'm also kinda worried because i feel a bit nauseous and i've been feeling a little feverish too. but like you said, it's probably just a gas bubble right? if i take the oxy with the ibuprofen will that make it work better so i can just pass out and not feel it in the morning? i really dont want to deal with doctors and hospitals rn",
